{"tag":"section","attrib":{"id":"idd1aa321b-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3106"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3106"},"text":"§ 3106.","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Dates for submittal of various annual and semiannual reports to the congressional intelligence committees","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idd1aa321c-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3106/a"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"a"},"text":"(a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Annual reports","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The date for the submittal to the congressional intelligence committees of the following annual reports shall be the date each year provided in subsection (c)(1):","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idd1aa321d-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3106/a/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The annual report of the Inspectors General of the intelligence community on proposed resources and activities of their offices required by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t5/s416/h"},"text":"section 416(h) of title 5","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idd1aa321e-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3106/a/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The annual report on certifications for immunity in interdiction of aircraft engaged in illicit drug trafficking required by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t22/s2291–4/c/2"},"text":"section 2291–4(c)(2) of title 22","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idd1aa321f-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3106/a/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The annual report on activities under the David L. Boren National Security Education Act of 1991 (title VIII of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/183"},"text":"Public Law 102–183","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s1901"},"text":"50 U.S.C. 1901","children":[],"tail":" et seq.) required by section 806(a) of that Act ("},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s1906/a"},"text":"50 U.S.C. 1906(a)","children":[],"tail":")."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idd1aa3220-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3106/a/4"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"4"},"text":"(4)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The annual report on hiring and retention of minority employees in the intelligence community required by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s3050/a"},"text":"section 3050(a) of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idd1aa3221-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3106/a/5"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"5"},"text":"(5)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The annual report on financial intelligence on terrorist assets required by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s3055"},"text":"section 3055 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idd1aa3222-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3106/a/6"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"6"},"text":"(6)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" An annual report submitted under ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s3059/d/1"},"text":"section 3059(d)(1) of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idd1aa3223-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3106/b"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"b"},"text":"(b)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Semiannual reports","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":"The dates for the submittal to the congressional intelligence committees of the following semiannual reports shall be the dates each year provided in subsection (c)(2):","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idd1aa3224-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3106/b/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The semiannual reports on decisions not to prosecute certain violations of law under the Classified Information Procedures Act (18 U.S.C. App.) as required by section 13 of that Act.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idd1aa3225-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3106/b/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The semiannual reports on the disclosure of information and consumer reports to the Federal Bureau of Investigation for counterintelligence purposes required by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s1681u/h/2"},"text":"section 1681u(h)(2) of title 15","children":[],"tail":"."},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"idref":"fn002080"},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"type":"footnote","id":"fn002080"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{},"text":"1","children":[],"tail":" See References in Text note below."}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idd1aa3226-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3106/b/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The semiannual provision of information on requests for financial information for foreign counterintelligence purposes required by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t12/s3414/a/5/C"},"text":"section 3414(a)(5)(C) of title 12","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idd1aa3227-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3106/c"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"c"},"text":"(c)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Submittal dates for reports","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idd1aa3228-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3106/c/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Except as provided in subsection (d), each annual report listed in subsection (a) shall be submitted not later than February 1.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idd1aa3229-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3106/c/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Except as provided in subsection (d), each semiannual report listed in subsection (b) shall be submitted not later than February 1 and August 1.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subsection","attrib":{"id":"idd1aa322a-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3106/d"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"d"},"text":"(d)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":" Postponement of submittal","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idd1aa322b-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3106/d/1"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"1"},"text":"(1)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"chapeau","attrib":{},"text":" Subject to paragraph (3), the date for the submittal of—","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idd1aa322c-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3106/d/1/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" an annual report listed in subsection (a) may be postponed until March 1; and","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idd1aa322d-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3106/d/1/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" a semiannual report listed in subsection (b) may be postponed until March 1 or September 1, as the case may be,","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n\n"},{"tag":"continuation","attrib":{},"text":"if the official required to submit such report submits to the congressional intelligence committees a written notification of such postponement.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idd1aa322e-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3106/d/2"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"2"},"text":"(2)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idd1aa322f-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3106/d/2/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" Notwithstanding any other provision of law and subject to paragraph (3), the date for the submittal to the congressional intelligence committees of any report described in subparagraph (B) may be postponed by not more than 30 days from the date otherwise specified in the provision of law for the submittal of such report if the official required to submit such report submits to the congressional intelligence committees a written notification of such postponement.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idd1aa3230-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3106/d/2/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" A report described in this subparagraph is any report on intelligence or intelligence-related activities of the United States Government that is submitted under a provision of law requiring the submittal of only a single report.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"paragraph","attrib":{"id":"idd1aa3231-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3106/d/3"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"3"},"text":"(3)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idd1aa3232-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3106/d/3/A"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"A"},"text":"(A)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" The date for the submittal of a report whose submittal is postponed under paragraph (1) or (2) may be postponed beyond the time provided for the submittal of such report under such paragraph if the official required to submit such report submits to the congressional intelligence committees a written certification that preparation and submittal of such report at such time will impede the work of officers or employees of the intelligence community in a manner that will be detrimental to the national security of the United States.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"subparagraph","attrib":{"id":"idd1aa3233-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e","identifier":"/us/usc/t50/s3106/d/3/B"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"num","attrib":{"value":"B"},"text":"(B)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"content","attrib":{},"text":" A certification with respect to a report under subparagraph (A) shall include a proposed submittal date for such report, and such report shall be submitted not later than that date.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"sourceCredit","attrib":{"id":"idd1aa3234-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":"(","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/act/1947-07-26/ch343"},"text":"July 26, 1947, ch. 343","children":[],"tail":", title V, § 507, as added "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/306/tVIII/s811/a/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 107–306, title VIII, § 811(a)(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2002-11-27"},"text":"Nov. 27, 2002","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/116/2418"},"text":"116 Stat. 2418","children":[],"tail":"; amended "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/177/tIII/s361"},"text":"Pub. L. 108–177, title III, § 361","children":[],"tail":"("},{"tag":"i","attrib":{},"text":"l","children":[],"tail":"), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2003-12-13"},"text":"Dec. 13, 2003","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/117/2626"},"text":"117 Stat. 2626","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/111/259/tIII/s349"},"text":"Pub. L. 111–259, title III, § 349","children":[],"tail":", title V, § 501(b)(3), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2010-10-07"},"text":"Oct. 7, 2010","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/124/2700"},"text":"124 Stat. 2700","children":[],"tail":", 2739; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/112/277/tIII"},"text":"Pub. L. 112–277, title III","children":[],"tail":", §§ 309(b)(2), 310(b)(1), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2013-01-14"},"text":"Jan. 14, 2013","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/126/2474"},"text":"126 Stat. 2474","children":[],"tail":", 2475; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/126/tIII/s329/c/3"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–126, title III, § 329(c)(3)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2014-07-07"},"text":"July 7, 2014","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/128/1407"},"text":"128 Stat. 1407","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/113/dM/tVII/s701/c/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–113, div. M, title VII, § 701(c)(2)","children":[],"tail":", (3), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2015-12-18"},"text":"Dec. 18, 2015","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/129/2929"},"text":"129 Stat. 2929","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/92/dE/tLIII/s5322/c"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–92, div. E, title LIII, § 5322(c)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2019-12-20"},"text":"Dec. 20, 2019","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/133/2130"},"text":"133 Stat. 2130","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/263/dF/tLXVIII/s6824/a/6"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–263, div. F, title LXVIII, § 6824(a)(6)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2022-12-23"},"text":"Dec. 23, 2022","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/136/3615"},"text":"136 Stat. 3615","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/286/s4/b/100"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–286, § 4(b)(100)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2022-12-27"},"text":"Dec. 27, 2022","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/136/4353"},"text":"136 Stat. 4353","children":[],"tail":"; "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/119/60/dF/tLXVIII/s6801/a/1/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 119–60, div. F, title LXVIII, § 6801(a)(1)(B)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2025-12-18"},"text":"Dec. 18, 2025","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/139/1652"},"text":"139 Stat. 1652","children":[],"tail":".)"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"notes","attrib":{"type":"uscNote","id":"idd1aa3235-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"prospectiveAmendment","id":"idd1aa3236-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendment of Subsection (a)","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/119/60/dF/tLXVIII/s6801/a/1/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 119–60, div. F, title LXVIII, § 6801(a)(1)(B)","children":[],"tail":", (C), "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2025-12-18"},"text":"Dec. 18, 2025","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/139/1652"},"text":"139 Stat. 1652","children":[],"tail":", provided that, effective on "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2026-12-31"},"text":"Dec. 31, 2026","children":[],"tail":", subsection (a) of this section is amended as follows:"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"(1) by striking paragraph (5); and","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"(2) by redesignating paragraph (6) as paragraph (5).","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"See 2025 Amendment note below.","children":[],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"role":"crossHeading","topic":"editorialNotes","id":"idd1aa3237-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"b","attrib":{},"text":"Editorial Notes","children":[],"tail":null}],"tail":null}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"referencesInText","id":"idd1aa3238-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":"\n","children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"References in Text","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The David L. Boren National Security Education Act of 1991, referred to in subsec. (a)(3), is title VIII of ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/102/183"},"text":"Pub. L. 102–183","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1991-12-04"},"text":"Dec. 4, 1991","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/105/1271"},"text":"105 Stat. 1271","children":[],"tail":", which is classified generally to chapter 37 (§ 1901 et seq.) of this title. For complete classification of this Act to the Code, see "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s1901/a"},"text":"section 1901(a) of this title","children":[],"tail":" and Tables."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"The Classified Information Procedures Act, referred to in subsec. (b)(1), is ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/96/456"},"text":"Pub. L. 96–456","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"1980-10-15"},"text":"Oct. 15, 1980","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/94/2025"},"text":"94 Stat. 2025","children":[],"tail":", which is set out in the Appendix to Title 18, Crimes and Criminal Procedure."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s1681u/h/2"},"text":"Section 1681u(h)(2) of title 15","children":[],"tail":", referred to in subsec. (b)(2), was in the original “section 624(h)(2) of the Fair Credit Reporting Act”, which was translated as reading “section 626(h)(2) of the Fair Credit Reporting Act”, to reflect the probable intent of Congress and the renumbering of section 624 as 626 by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/107/56/s358/g/1/A"},"text":"section 358(g)(1)(A) of Pub. L. 107–56","children":[],"tail":" and "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/108/159/s214/a/1"},"text":"section 214(a)(1) of Pub. L. 108–159","children":[],"tail":". "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s1681u/h"},"text":"Section 1681u(h) of title 15","children":[],"tail":" was subsequently redesignated "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t15/s1681u/i"},"text":"section 1681u(i) of title 15","children":[],"tail":" by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/23/tV/s503/c/1"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–23, title V, § 503(c)(1)","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"date","attrib":{"date":"2015-06-02"},"text":"June 2, 2015","children":[],"tail":", "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/stat/129/290"},"text":"129 Stat. 290","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"codification","id":"idd1aa3239-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Codification","children":[],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Section was formerly classified to ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s415b"},"text":"section 415b of this title","children":[],"tail":" prior to editorial reclassification and renumbering as this section. Some section numbers of this title referenced in amendment notes below reflect the classification of such sections prior to their editorial reclassification."}],"tail":"\n"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"note","attrib":{"topic":"amendments","id":"idd1aa323a-47c4-11f1-8bcf-c89722bddd2e"},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"heading","attrib":{},"text":"Amendments","children":[],"tail":null},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2025—Subsec. (a)(5), (6). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/119/60"},"text":"Pub. L. 119–60","children":[],"tail":" redesignated par. (6) as (5) and struck out former par. (5) which read as follows: “The annual report on financial intelligence on terrorist assets required by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s3055"},"text":"section 3055 of this title","children":[],"tail":".”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2022—Subsec. (a)(1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/286"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–286","children":[],"tail":" substituted “"},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t5/s416/h"},"text":"section 416(h) of title 5","children":[],"tail":".” for “section 8H(g) of the Inspector General Act of 1978.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":null,"children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/117/263"},"text":"Pub. L. 117–263","children":[],"tail":" substituted “Inspectors General” for “Inspectors Generals”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2019—Subsec. (a)(6). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/116/92"},"text":"Pub. L. 116–92","children":[],"tail":" added par. (6)."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2015—Subsec. (a)(5), (6). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/113/s701/c/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–113, § 701(c)(2)","children":[],"tail":", redesignated par. (6) as (5) and struck out former par. (5) which read as follows: “The annual report on outside employment of employees of elements of the intelligence community required by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s3024/u/2"},"text":"section 3024(u)(2) of this title","children":[],"tail":".”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (c)(1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/114/113/s701/c/3"},"text":"Pub. L. 114–113, § 701(c)(3)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “subsection (a)” for “subsection (a)(1)”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2014—Subsec. (a). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/126/s329/c/3/A"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–126, § 329(c)(3)(A)","children":[],"tail":", in introductory provisions, struck out par. (1) designation before “The date” and substituted “subsection (c)(1)” for “subsection (c)(1)(A)”, redesignated subpars. (A) to (F) of former par. (1) as pars. (1) to (6), respectively, and struck out former par. (2) which read as follows: “The date for the submittal to the congressional intelligence committees of the annual report on the threat of attack on the United States from weapons of mass destruction required by "},{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s3050/b"},"text":"section 3050(b) of this title","children":[],"tail":" shall be the date each year provided in subsection (c)(1)(B).”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (c)(1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/126/s329/c/3/B"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–126, § 329(c)(3)(B)","children":[],"tail":", struck out subpar. (A) designation before “Except” and struck out subpar. (B) which read as follows: “Except as provided in subsection (d), the annual report listed in subsection (a)(2) shall be submitted not later than December 1.”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (d)(1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/113/126/s329/c/3/C"},"text":"Pub. L. 113–126, § 329(c)(3)(C)","children":[],"tail":", in subpar. (A), substituted “subsection (a)” for “subsection (a)(1)” and inserted “and” after “March 1;”, redesignated subpar. (C) as (B), and struck out former subpar. (B) which read as follows: “the annual report listed in subsection (a)(2) may be postponed until January 1; and”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"2013—Subsec. (a)(1). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/112/277/s310/b/1/A/i/I"},"text":"Pub. L. 112–277, § 310(b)(1)(A)(i)(I)","children":[],"tail":", (II), redesignated subpars. (B), (E), (F), (G), (H), and (I) as (A), (B), (C), (D), (E), and (F), respectively, and struck out former subpars. (A), (C), and (D) which read as follows:"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(A) The annual report on the protection of the identities of covert agents required by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s423"},"text":"section 423 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(C) The annual report on the acquisition of technology relating to weapons of mass destruction and advanced conventional munitions required by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s2366"},"text":"section 2366 of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(D) The annual report on commercial activities as security for intelligence collection required by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t10/s437/c"},"text":"section 437(c) of title 10","children":[],"tail":".”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(1)(D). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/112/277/s310/b/1/A/i/III"},"text":"Pub. L. 112–277, § 310(b)(1)(A)(i)(III)","children":[],"tail":", substituted “section 404i(a)” for “section 404i(c)”."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (a)(2). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/112/277/s310/b/1/A/ii"},"text":"Pub. L. 112–277, § 310(b)(1)(A)(ii)","children":[],"tail":", amended par. (2) generally. Prior to amendment, par. (2) read as follows: “The date for the submittal to the congressional intelligence committees of the following annual reports shall be the date each year provided in subsection (c)(1)(B):"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(A) The annual report on the safety and security of Russian nuclear facilities and nuclear military forces required by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s404i/a"},"text":"section 404i(a) of this title","children":[],"tail":"."}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"“(B) The annual report on the threat of attack on the United States from weapons of mass destruction required by ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/usc/t50/s404i/c"},"text":"section 404i(c) of this title","children":[],"tail":".”"}],"tail":"\n"},{"tag":"p","attrib":{},"text":"Subsec. (b). ","children":[{"tag":"ref","attrib":{"href":"/us/pl/112/277/s309/b/2"},"text":"Pub. L. 112–277, § 309(b)(2)","children":[],"tail":", redesignated pars. (2) to (4) as (1) to (3), respecti